metadata.name: Stream Liquid Nights #1
metadata.description: Stream Liquid Nights - 999 1/1 generative art piece NFT collection. Stream Liquid Nights is the latest and most advanced generative algorithm to date by using a continuously optimised code developed in Processing with Java. The main basis is a vortex algorithm, composed of aesthetically pleasing lines and curves. They run alongside the neighbouring lines and curves without causing a collision. Their intertwined paths form a vortex. Isn't life a vortex of destinies?
